{"tid":2430854,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"班主任好「出狩行獵」15歲男子慘被盯中 成圍獵目標","createTime":"2021-03-03T08:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T12:27:13.000Z","uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a51b962d45d819f397716c4b490733669338afc","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47ba44a92af2b95b8a4dd9c962975839c524285","tid":2430854,"uid":366530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fe89854443a8d52ada04a72e7ead3909925b14","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a47ba44a92af2b95b8a4dd9c962975839c524285","tid":2430854,"uid":366530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9mNSdP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9mNSdP.jpg&h=ba71fc73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31be9484e0b919a4809f5a55060e5f7a57009805","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:33:28.000Z","msg":"​乾隆二十年（1755年），這一年乾隆皇帝45歲，乾隆帝帶領着眾多的近親王公大臣在南苑獵場進行了一次田獵活動，在這場打獵遊戲中，乾隆皇帝一人就射中了八隻野兔，「是日凡中八兔。」乾隆非常開心，就命郎世寧等宮廷畫師將這次戰績繪製下來，並且親筆題詩三首於畫上。<br />\n<br />\n從畫上可以看出，乾隆皇帝神情專注，弓馬嫻熟，三名身穿黃馬甲的侍衛騎着駿馬跟隨乾隆打獵，一人在前圍堵，兩人騎馬跟着乾隆準備側後包抄；還有兩名侍衛下馬，各自撿拾已經中箭的戰利品，最後一人騎着雙馬在遠處等待，相信是準備隨時隨地準備換馬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://71a.xyz/bgGLLJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F71a.xyz%2FbgGLLJ&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiukngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=a39b44dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://71a.xyz/bgGLLJ</a>"},{"pid":"2a5d6899c41e371ceb096a8c0f1dbc4d1a9692f4","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaNhu1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaNhu1a.jpg&h=9127f0a7&s={SIZE}\" /> 黑狗婆∶我最愛行獵了！"},{"pid":"2c03275dc0745527823783e87cde083a888f3def","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"​2015年，這一年黑狗婆徐敏玲45歲，黑狗婆帶領着眾多的近親王公大臣在南苑獵場進行了一次田獵活動，在這場打獵遊戲中，黑狗婆一人就射中了八隻野兔，「是日凡中八兔。」黑狗婆非常開心，就命郎世寧等宮廷畫師將這次戰績繪製下來，並且親筆題詩三首於畫上。<br />\n<br />\n從畫上可以看出，黑狗婆神情專注，弓馬嫻熟，三名身穿黃馬甲的侍衛騎着駿馬跟隨黑狗婆打獵，一人在前圍堵，兩人騎馬跟着黑狗婆準備側後包抄；還有兩名侍衛下馬，各自撿拾已經中箭的戰利品，最後一人騎着雙馬在遠處等待，相信是準備隨時隨地準備換馬。"},{"pid":"b33aeaf49db042237dc0d5bc9fd63e5edaa6bb94","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"黑狗婆圍毆我只係無聊想立威。"},{"pid":"4a10a33ebf992210b460549d4e58e50255e221d6","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/STp0sSL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSTp0sSL.jpg&h=e354591b&s={SIZE}\" /> 黑狗婆只係想恃人多立威。"},{"pid":"4888d1a482577d8a57626d21d67f6cec770024e5","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"黑狗婆以為只要靠人多，就可以任意行獵。可惜，你選錯對象了。"},{"pid":"7a1ba95eaa5a7f908410552bce65660118227aab","tid":2430854,"uid":380120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"你選擇的行獵目標，是進擊的巨人。"},{"pid":"580aa0f18e24b3f6b1